channel.title: I somehow can't login! any ideas?
channel.description:
I have always managed to login to my server with My Client. So the first thing i did was trying to move the server to another comp(let's call that computer comp2) So on comp2 i entered another network and i changed the server ip to that network and i managed to login then i went to comp and changed the client.java to localhost and runned the server on that computer, but somehow i can't login!!
Any ideas ?
